Kryvyi Rih.title: Kryvyi Rih
Kryvyi Rih.byline: Kryvyi Rih (Ukrainian: Кривий Ріг, also transliterated Krivoy Rog from Russian: Кривой Рог), is an industrial city of 660,000 people in Dnipropetrovsk Oblast, Ukraine.
